Test/Pod version 1.45
=====================

This library's module, Test::Pod, provides an interface for validating POD in
module files.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

Dependencies
------------

Test::Pod requires the following modules:

* Pod::Simple 3.05
* Test::More 0.62
* Test::Builder::Tester 1.02
* File::Spec

